projects.name: Book Wallah
projects.description: User Registration and Authentication: Engineered a secure system for user account creation and login, ensuring data privacy and integrity. Book Listing: Developed functionality allowing users to list books available for exchange or lending, promoting a community-driven book-sharing platform. Book Search: Integrated an advanced search feature enabling users to find books by title, author, genre, and other criteria, enhancing user experience. Book Request: Implemented a feature that allows users to request to borrow books from other users, facilitating book exchanges.

projects.name: Stream Hub
projects.description: User Authentication: Implemented secure user authentication mechanisms to protect user data and manage access. Video Streaming: Developed functionalities for streaming videos, enabling users to upload, view, and interact with multimedia content. Social Interactions: Added features for posting tweets, allowing users to engage in social interactions around the video content.

projects.name: Chat App
projects.description: Messaging Platform: Created a robust messaging application using Firebase Authentication for secure user login and identity management. Real-time Messaging: Utilized Firebase Realtime Database to enable real-time messaging, ensuring seamless and instant communication between users.
